message.text:
hello, OPC! 

‼️crowdsourcing for FA in Communication Planning‼️

LF: IHSN students part of the IHSN SC well-versed w the inner workings of the org, such as processing documents and organizing events for the insti, etc. 

📌 can be current or former members of the SC 
📌 open for students from any program under IHSN 
(we also need students from BS Nutrition and Dietetics and BS Pharmacy) 

It will only be a quick written interview thru chat or gdocs w 5-10 questions abt the organization only 🤓

all info gathered will be confidential and only be used in academic setting

pls send me a pm if u're interested in helping us! 🥺🙏
